{"tid":2007760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[5名未成年手足\b被控暴動提堂！] 5月9號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-05-08T13:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T01:40:46.000Z","uid":292499,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"69594144f429d88ae4fe7424c358e849fae251b9","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 5 月 9 日 星期六】<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤李(20) #提堂（#0816上水 / #0817打鼓嶺 管有攻擊性武器:捧球棍、鐵通等）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 8 樓 7 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕥10:30<br />\n👥5名未成年手足(14-15) #提堂（#1118油麻地 暴動）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 2 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕦11:30<br />\n👤陳(29) #提堂（#0713上水 非法集結、襲警:涉推撞便衣警陳國深的頭盔）"},{"pid":"79163fc722d720628f68209dd9c2a8e54d77724c","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=248e98f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"6051d9fea2f19263dfbc5a4378b4572e0d305359","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=d86a7ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=a91eb5d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"2882244ac995e9ff39eb899121eace865c3dde65","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZDJAee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZDJAee.jpg&h=42d83846&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d770998250674e7acf9a4c50b5d631cca3b4bc2","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"61fad27a344cfb82bb23f45c6cc567704b3586f9","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n粉嶺裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界東</strong><br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺法院大樓] **不建議<br />\n上水：79K       [璧峰路]<br />\n打鼓嶺：79K   [粉嶺法院大樓]<br />\n大老山：277X [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界西</strong><br />\n屯門：261       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n青衣：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大欖：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n藍田站、觀塘道、彩虹邨：277X  [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后：673 [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺相對少對外交通，其他地區需使用黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"a7ef50df0a1dbaca0a774c6baa8c18fe9f2c860d","tid":2007760,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3650f2de9cc8bd63d2468e9c28131c13df639732","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"【保釋及送車位置】<br />\n<br />\n✵送車位位於法院停車場🅿️<br />\n✵揾唔到就圍住法院兜一圈⭕️<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門<br />\n**唯一送車遮陣出出入入都係同一個位<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"95a5198499d9f3026eb56dd140350bb2290d4c7c","tid":2007760,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae5668a72737279454b4c330e4d2d821c1f0449","tid":2007760,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ef50df0a1dbaca0a774c6baa8c18fe9f2c860d","tid":2007760,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53ce57c0b789cf7036ed3a0b8f93ec74d991d45","tid":2007760,"uid":26